Rebuild notes

The WASM module is built with Emscripten and statically links the libraries above.
See docs/wasm-deps.md for dependency versions, build order, and the required
Poppler Emscripten patch (scripts/poppler-emscripten.patch).

Native macOS builds may use Homebrew Poppler instead; the same Poppler version
(26.04.0) is recommended so behavior matches the WASM build.
